{
  "stem": "10181.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, my sister was four years older, so she-- I guess emotionally for her, it was a little different.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, for me, it was-- it wasn't-- it wasn't fun.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was strange, but I-- I knew-- I knew them well.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Adolf, I knew him well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and-- and there are two cousins.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Had two cousins there, two-- two girls, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They both were older.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I didn't mind going there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I felt-- I felt OK.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I'm sure I missed my mother, but I very quickly, you know, made friends, learned Dutch.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "At that age, you learn very quickly by playing outside.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I started going to school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's a regular-- in that area, they had always two schools.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Most of Holland has two [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There's a very big Catholic population.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They have a Catholic school and then a general school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So everybody who wasn't Catholic went to the general school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So all the Jewish kids of course, went to the general school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in that town-- in that little town, there were not-- were not that many Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In Holland, they-- the Jews in almost every-- every town, every little place were Dutch Jews, not-- not German Jews.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in this particular little town, there were just a few families.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But when the German Jews came, that's when the Jewish population relatively grew.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It still wasn't very big.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, it wasn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was no-- there was no proper synagogue.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was like a little room, you know, where they prayed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- and I would say the majority were German Jews, yeah, not-- not Dutch Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But life was, except for my mother not being there, was very normal, you know, because Holland wasn't at war or anything.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And neither was Germany [INAUDIBLE] still.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But, you know, there was no anti-Semitic laws.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I mean, the Jews were treated like everybody else.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The only thing is we were-- we were foreigners, basically.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We weren't Dutch.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But even that didn't really bother us, except there was sort of an incident which I remember well because it sort of was, you know, a big thing.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I had two uncles who came to live at the same house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "These were the husbands of two sisters of my father.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "My father had a lot of brothers and sisters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There were seven all together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So two of his sisters, their husbands, who were cousins coincidentally-- with the name of Hes-- they came to-- after the Kristallnacht, after they were released from prison, they came to stay in Holland while their wives made arrangements to get a visa to go to Chile.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They had a-- they could get-- they could go to Chile.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They got visa to go to Chile, and they found this through my mother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "My mother had the opportunity to go to Chile, but she felt that Chile was the end of the world.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Didn't want to go to Chile.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "She was looking for North America, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "She wasn't looking for Chile.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "She didn't-- she thought it was too far away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So she told them about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And they made arrangements and-- and got the visa to go to Chile.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "In the meanwhile, the two men were staying with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, from Germany.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From a different town.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A town called [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a small town, in those days especially.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So what happening?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Obviously, they must have crossed the border illegally.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And also, my uncle must have done something to help them which wasn't-- the Germans didn't like.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know exactly what he did.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I guess it must have been monetary again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, even though they didn't have much money-- they weren't very wealthy people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But he must have done something because the Dutch came to arrest them and-- and my uncle.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they did it under the pressure from the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they came and picked him up, which I remember because it was a shock, you know, my uncle being arrested.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And both-- all uncles.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, you look-- look upon uncles as, you know, something special.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and were, actually.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] All of them-- I was spoiled by them, actually, being the little boy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were sent to a prison further south called [INAUDIBLE] where they were kept.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then, those two uncles, I didn't see them again then because they were-- when they were released, they went via Italy and to-- to South America, to Chile.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my uncle was released fairly soon afterwards at night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The Dutch didn't really want to imprison him apparently, but imprisoned him under the pressure of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there were some Nazis in town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, Holland had a fairly large, relatively speaking, Nazi party.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Active.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
